      "description": "Technical Council (9 members, proposal rights only). Stewardship Custodians (11 members, binding veto). Smart Contract Treasury (automatic execution, no admin key). Survivability-class amendments require proposer exit, 180-day clock from submission, dual-vote ratification at 75% both chambers, and one-year institution ban on filling the proposer's vacated seat.",
